The paper deals with removing rain streaks from outdoor videos, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The proposed method involves incorporating sparsity and low-rank properties, which are common techniques in machine learning and optimization, suggesting that the paper could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of regularization and optimization methods also suggests that the paper could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper involves processing videos, which could also suggest that it belongs to cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper involves solving a complicated optimization problem, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.IT (Information Theory).
